@0    = ~Help me... Help me... p-please...~
@1    = ~Who are you?~
@2    = ~Begone beggar! I have no money for you.~
@3    = ~I help no one but myself! Leave me.~
@4    = ~It's me... Agal. Don't you recognize me?~
