@10   = ~This is terrible. I will avenge you, Agal. Know this as your moment to die nears.~
@11   = ~One less mouth to feed in the world. No loss there.~
@12   = ~I... I am sorry... My eyes close...~
@13   = ~Thank you... friend.~
@14   = ~I... I led you into these tunnels... then I met up with... a being.~
